    <h2 {...{
      "id": "database-servers"
    }}>{`Database Servers`}</h2>
    <p>{`Using a separate `}<strong parentName="p">{`Database Server`}</strong>{` to handle all database queries has advantages like better `}<strong parentName="p">{`performance`}</strong>{` and the possibility to `}<strong parentName="p">{`restore`}</strong>{` to a specific time.
All major cloud providers are offering MySQL database services.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "add-database-server"
    }}>{`Add Database Server`}</h3>
    <p>{`To add a new `}<strong parentName="p">{`Database Server`}</strong>{` do the following steps:`}</p>
    <p>{`1) Login into the `}<strong parentName="p">{`CloudPanel`}</strong>{` as `}<strong parentName="p">{`User`}</strong>{` with admin rights.`}</p>
    <p>{`2) Go to the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Admin Area`}</strong>{` by clicking on `}<strong parentName="p">{`Admin Area`}</strong>{` top right.`}</p>
    <p>{`3) In the left menu, click on `}<strong parentName="p">{`Database Servers`}</strong>{` and click on the button `}<strong parentName="p">{`Add Database Server`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <img class="border" src={useBaseUrl('img/v1/admin/database_servers/database_servers.png')} /> <br /> <br />
    <p>{`Enter the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Host`}</strong>{`, `}<strong parentName="p">{`Port`}</strong>{`, `}<strong parentName="p">{`User Name`}</strong>{` and `}<strong parentName="p">{`Password`}</strong>{` of the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Database Server`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`The `}<strong parentName="p">{`User`}</strong>{` should have super privileges like the `}<strong parentName="p">{`root`}</strong>{` user.`}</p>
    <img class="border" src={useBaseUrl('img/v1/admin/database_servers/add_database_server.png')} /> <br /> <br />
