              }}></path></svg></span>{`MySQL Versions`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-content"
      }}><p parentName="div">{`Only `}<strong parentName="p">{`MySQL 5.5`}</strong>{`, `}<strong parentName="p">{`5.6`}</strong>{` and `}<strong parentName="p">{`5.7`}</strong>{` are supported. `}<strong parentName="p">{`MySQL 8.0`}</strong>{` will be supported in the next major `}<strong parentName="p">{`CloudPanel`}</strong>{` version.`}</p></div></div>
